Billy Bletcher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billy_Bletcher 0 William Bletcher (September 24, 1894 – January 5, 1979) was an American actor and voice actor. He is mostly well known for his role as the voice of Pete in the Mickey Mouse short films from 1932 to 1954.
